@startuml C4_Quality_Guards
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml

title YAWL Quality Gate - H-Guards Validation

Boundary(generated_code, "Generated Code") {
    Component(java_files, "Java Files", "Code", "Generated classes")
}

Boundary(guard_validation, "H-Guards Validation") {
    Component(h_todo, "H_TODO Detector", "Regex", "TODO/FIXME markers")
    Component(h_mock, "H_MOCK Detector", "Regex+SPARQL", "Mock implementations")
    Component(h_stub, "H_STUB Detector", "SPARQL", "Empty returns")
    Component(h_empty, "H_EMPTY Detector", "SPARQL", "No-op bodies")
    Component(h_fallback, "H_FALLBACK Detector", "SPARQL", "Silent catch")
    Component(h_lie, "H_LIE Detector", "SPARQL", "Code ≠ docs")
    Component(h_silent, "H_SILENT Detector", "Regex", "Log instead throw")
}

Boundary(validation_engine, "Validation Engine") {
    Component(hypervalidator, "HyperStandardsValidator", "Orchestrator", "Runs all guards")
    Component(receipt, "GuardReceipt", "Report", "JSON report")
}

Boundary(gates, "Gates") {
    Component(pass_gate, "PASS", "Green", "No violations")
    Component(fail_gate, "FAIL", "Red", "Violations found")
}

java_files --> h_todo: Scans for
java_files --> h_mock: Scans for
java_files --> h_stub: Scans for
java_files --> h_empty: Scans for
java_files --> h_fallback: Scans for
java_files --> h_lie: Scans for
java_files --> h_silent: Scans for

h_todo --> hypervalidator: Reports
h_mock --> hypervalidator: Reports
h_stub --> hypervalidator: Reports
h_empty --> hypervalidator: Reports
h_fallback --> hypervalidator: Reports
h_lie --> hypervalidator: Reports
h_silent --> hypervalidator: Reports

hypervalidator --> receipt: Generates
receipt --> pass_gate: No violations
receipt --> fail_gate: Violations found

Note as N1
H-Guards enforce "no fakes" principle
7 patterns:
1. TODO/FIXME markers
2. Mock implementations
3. Empty returns
4. No-op methods
5. Silent degradation
6. Documentation lies
7. Logging instead of throwing

Gate: Must be GREEN to proceed
End note

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml
